.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, mirinda, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, paramedic, social-worker, writer
There are 4 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, italian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, aconite, daisy, dahlia
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 2. the egyptian is the social-worker##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 4. the librarian is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 5. the person drinking juice is the writer##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 7. the person who growsmarigold is the italian##1
 8. the writer is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the british##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | sprite    | juice      |
| Job           | social-worker | librarian | paramedic | writer     |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | italian   | british   | indonesian |
| Flower           | dahlia         | marigold       | daisy  | aconite       |

