.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, orange, pineapple, spinach
House: cottage, art-deco, craftsman, cape-cod
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, manager, musician
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, skiing, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the craftsman house is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person eating spinach##2
 3. the manager is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the librarian is the person eating kiwi##1
 5. the bartender is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 6. the cottage house is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating orange is the bartender##1
 8. the craftsman house is the librarian##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
10. the librarian is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
12. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | pineapple    | spinach      | kiwi          | orange    |
| House   | art-deco | cape-cod       | craftsman | cottage |
| Job     | musician     | manager      | librarian     | bartender |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | snowboarding | skiing        | cricket   |

