 9. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
10. the egyptian is on the far right##1
11. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
12. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
