The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, surfing, tennis
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
 3. the chef is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 6. the owner of the rabbit is the bartender##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
 8. the chef is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3
10. the bartender is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the pilot is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |    3     |    4     |
