.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, juice, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, singing, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, sports, western
City: san-francisco, paris, berlin, new-york
 1. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
10. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice       | hot-chocolate | 7up        | milk        |
| Hobby         | video-games | singing       | card-games | photography |
| Movie-Genre   | western     | satire        | mystery    | sports      |
| City         | paris     | berlin    | new-york | san-francisco   |

